name: intelligentsocketdataloggerconfiggenerator
description: This is a config editor for [Technik-Tueftler/IntelligentSocketDatalogger](https://github.com/Technik-Tueftler/IntelligentSocketDatalogger).   **Go to https://isdledit.jojojux.de/ to test!**   Load a file using the import button to edit or start with an empty file using the editing options.   Press the save button to save your current inputs to a isdl_config.json in your downloads folder.   **All files are process locally in your browser, this website is fully client-side.**
